title: Hands_on Exercise 1: Geospatial Data Wrangling with R
text: In this hands-on exercise, I learn how to import and wrangle geospatial data using appropriate R packages.

title: Hands_on Exercise 1: Geospatial Data Wrangling with R
text:
Getting Started
The code chunk below install and load sf and tidyverse packages into R environment.

pacman::p_load(sf, tidyverse)
